title: Musician covers every part of "Africa" by Toto
text:
Musician covers every part of "Africa" by Toto Jan 30, 2017 Next 
Toto's "Africa" might be one of the most covered songs on the internet - and for good reason. Not only is it a huge crowd pleaser, but the fact that it uses so many different instruments makes it great for a group. That's why this guy's cover is so impressive. He plays everything from the recorder to the egg and sounds just as good as, if not better than, a professional band. 0 Shares
